: 2750 lbs Time Since Last Inspection: 102 Hours Engines: 1 Reciprocating Airframe Total Time: 4206 Hours Engine Manufacturer: CONTINENTAL ELT: Installed, not activated Engine Model/Series: E-225 Registered Owner: SAFETY DEVICES INC.
